    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing straightforward transportation. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car remains roadworthy, there are visible signs of age including some paint fading, minor interior upholstery wear, and a few small dings on the exterior. It has been regularly serviced, though a new owner should expect some upcoming routine maintenance tasks like brake pad replacement or tire rotations in the near future. Overall, it\u2019s a solid, honest car that offers practical value without the premium price of a newer model.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission are solid and the car runs well, it shows its age with some significant paint fading on the hood and several minor dents along the passenger side. The interior has visible wear on the driver's seat and the air conditioning is functional but takes a moment to cool down. It\u2019s a dependable car that has been well-maintained mechanically, though it would benefit from some cosmetic attention and minor suspension work in the future.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience perfection with this incredible, showroom-ready vehicle! It is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving exactly like it just left the dealership. Every detail, from the flawless exterior to the pristine interior, has been meticulously cared for, offering a truly like-new experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
